         <div xml:lang="gml">
            <p n="a#1" xml:space="preserve">Van Godes gnaden wy Alleff / hertoge tho Schlesewick / unde <app><lem>greue</lem><rdg><q>greve</q>, Kortholt, Femaria desolata (1695), p. 42</rdg></app> tho Holsten / Stormeren / unde tho Schowenborch / bekennen unde bet{ue}gen openbahre an
      desme breue vor <app><lem>alszweme</lem><rdg><q>alsweme</q>, Kortholt, Femaria desolata (1695), p. 42</rdg></app> de ene zen edder horen <app><lem>leszen</lem><rdg>både Kortholt, Femaria desolata (1673), p. 25, og Kortholt, Femaria desolata (1695), p.
          42, læser <q>letzen</q></rdg></app> / dat wy unsen <app><lem>armen</lem><rdg><q>vramen</q>, Ab1; <q>framen</q>, Ac1</rdg></app> l{ue}den / de van <app><lem>deme koninghe van Dennemarcken</lem><rdg><q>dem köning Erich van Dennemarcken</q>, Rep. nr. 6086 l.l.; <q>koning Erick</q>, Ab1;
            <q>koning Ericke</q>, Ac1</rdg></app> van <app><lem>vnseme</lem><rdg><q>unseme</q>, Kortholt, Femaria desolata (1695), p. 43</rdg></app>
      <app><lem>lande</lem><rdg><q>vnseme lande</q>, Rep. nr. 6086 l.l. læser <q>unsern lande</q></rdg></app> Vemeren <app><lem>vordreuen</lem><rdg><q>verdreven</q>, Kortholt, Femaria desolata (1695), p. 43; <q>gedreven</q>, Ab1;
            <q>ghedreven</q>, Ac1</rdg></app> worden / <app><lem>gheorlouet</lem><rdg><q>gheorlovet</q>, Kortholt, Femaria desolata (1695), p. 43</rdg></app>
      <app><lem>unde gh{ue}nt</lem><rdg><q>unde gegunnet</q>, Ab1; <q>unde gegunnet</q>, Ac1</rdg></app> hebben / dat <app><lem>de ghennen</lem><rdg><q>de jennen</q>, Rep. nr. 6086 l.l.; <q>en islick</q>, Ab1; <q>islich</q>, Ac1</rdg></app> / de dar noch <app><lem>van</lem><rdg><q>aff</q>, Ab1; <q>aff</q>, Ac1; <q>af</q>, Rep. nr. 6086 l.l</rdg></app>
      <app><lem>leuen</lem><rdg><q>leven</q>, Kortholt, Femaria desolata (1695), p. 43</rdg></app> / <app><lem>ein jewelick</lem><rdg><q>ein jeder</q>, Rep. nr. 6086 l.l</rdg></app>
      <app><lem>vppe</lem><rdg><q>uppe</q>, Kortholt, Femaria desolata (1695), p. 43</rdg></app> s{ue}n erve unde uppe dat syne wedder buwen moghe / unde willen wy unde <app><lem>vnse</lem><rdg><q>unse</q>, Kortholt, Femaria desolata (1695), p. 43</rdg></app> eruen enen <app><lem>yewelcken</lem><rdg><q>jewelcken</q>, Kortholt, Femaria desolata (1695), p. 43; <q>jeglichen</q>, Rep. nr.
          6086 l.l</rdg></app> by older <app><lem>rechticheid</lem><rdg><q>rechticheyt</q>, Ab1; <q>gerechticheyt</q>, Ac1; <q>gerechticheitt</q>, Rep. nr.
          6086 l.l</rdg></app> unde <app><lem>wonheid</lem><rdg><q>wonheyt</q>, Ac1; <q>gewonheyt</q>, Ab1; <q>gewandheidt</q>, Rep. nr. 6086 l.l</rdg></app>
      <app><lem>laten</lem><rdg><q>tho lathende</q>, Rep. nr. 6086 l.l</rdg></app> / unde by <app><lem>alleme</lem><rdg>Kortholt, Femaria desolata (1695), p. 43, læser herfor fejlagtigt <q>alleine</q></rdg></app> rechte beholden / allze <app><lem>vnse</lem><rdg><q>unse</q>, Kortholt, Femaria desolata (1695), p. 43</rdg></app> vorvaren vore unde <app><lem>vnse</lem><rdg><q>unse</q>, Kortholt, Femaria desolata (1695), p. 43</rdg></app> elderen en in vortyden <app><lem>geuen</lem><rdg><q>geven</q>, Kortholt, Femaria desolata (1695), p. 43</rdg></app> hadden / unde willen <app><lem>en</lem><rdg><q>ehm</q>, Rep. nr. 6086 l.l</rdg></app> ok gerne van nuto <app><lem>S{ue}nten Michels dage</lem><rdg><q>Michaelis dagh</q>, Rep. nr. 6086 l.l</rdg></app>
      <app><lem>an</lem><rdg><q>van nuto S{ue}nten Michels dage an</q>, dvs. fra 29. september 1424</rdg></app> / vort <app><lem>ouer</lem><rdg><q>over</q>, Kortholt, Femaria desolata (1695), p. 43</rdg></app> vyff jahren <app><lem>vryheid</lem><rdg><q>freyheidt</q>, Rep. nr. 6086 l.l</rdg></app>
      <app><lem>geuen</lem><rdg><q>geven</q>, Kortholt, Femaria desolata (1695), p. 43</rdg></app> / dat ze <app><lem>vns</lem><rdg><q>uns</q>, Kortholt, Femaria desolata (1695), p. 43</rdg></app> denne unde <app><lem>vnsen eruen</lem><rdg><q>unsen erven</q>, Kortholt, Femaria desolata (1695), p. 43</rdg></app>
      <app><lem>unde</lem><rdg><q>und</q>, Kortholt, Femaria desolata (1695), p. 43</rdg></app> nakomelingen darna wan de vyff jahr umme kommen s{ue}n / schat / rente / pacht / beede
      / tyns unde <app><lem>gulde</lem><rdg><q>gelde</q>, Rep. nr. 6086 l.l</rdg></app>
      <app><lem>daruan</lem><rdg><q>darvan</q>, Kortholt, Femaria desolata (1695), p. 44</rdg></app>
      <app><lem>geuen</lem><rdg><q>geven</q>, Kortholt, Femaria desolata (1695), p. 44</rdg></app>.</p>
            <p n="a#2" xml:space="preserve">Desto groterer witlicheid hebbe wy <app><lem>hertoch</lem><rdg><q>hertog</q>, Kortholt, Femaria desolata (1695), p. 44</rdg></app> Alleff vorbenomed <app><lem>vnse</lem><rdg><q>unse</q>, Kortholt, Femaria desolata (1695), p. 44</rdg></app> jngezegel mid witschop vor <app><lem>deszen</lem><rdg><q>dessen</q>, Kortholt, Femaria desolata (1695), p. 44</rdg></app> breff ghehenged laten / de <app><lem>geuen</lem><rdg><q>geven</q>, Kortholt, Femaria desolata (1695), p. 44</rdg></app> isz na Godes <app><lem>bort</lem><rdg>Kortholt, Femaria desolata (1695), p. 44, læser herfor fejlagtigt <q>wort</q></rdg></app>
      <app><lem>veertein</lem><rdg><q>veer tein</q>, Kortholt, Femaria desolata (1695), p. 44</rdg></app> hundert jahr / darna an deme veer unde twintigesten jahre / des ersten sondages in der
      vasten.</p>
